# Registry Files Are Auto-Generated — Do NOT Edit

These files are produced by `generate-registry.js` reading `components.yaml` + source files. Any manual edits will be overwritten on the next build.

## What to do instead

| Goal | Correct action |
|------|---------------|
| Add / update a component | Edit `src/components/ui/<name>.tsx` |
| Change component metadata | Edit `packages/cli/components.yaml` |
| Regenerate registry | Run `npm run build` in `packages/cli/` |

## Regeneration command

```bash
cd packages/cli
npm run generate-registry   # regenerate only
npm run build               # full pipeline (validate → generate → tsup → verify)
```

**Never commit changes to these files directly.**
